Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • ss.qwirkle.common.controller.Game
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientGame, SingleplayerGame

    public abstract class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller class for the game. Starts matches and handles communication between the UI and the rest of the system.
